item.title: Docs: Node Exporter
item.description:
Common Labels

标签名 示例值
job [opsaid-agent,node_exporter]
instance [localhost]

Metrics

nginx_ingress_controller_bytes_sent histogram The number of bytes sent to a client

nginx_ingress_controller_bytes_sent_count

nginx_ingress_controller_nginx_process_oldest_start_time_seconds gauge start time in seconds since 1970/01/01
nginx_ingress_controller_nginx_process_read_bytes_total counter number of bytes read

nginx_ingress_controller_nginx_process_resident_memory_bytes gauge number of bytes of memory in use

nginx_ingress_controller_nginx_process_write_bytes_total counter number of bytes written

Metrics

名称 类型 描述
burrow_kafka_consumer_current_offset gauge Latest offset that Burrow is storing for this partition
burrow_kafka_consumer_lag_total gauge The sum of all partition current lag values for the group
burrow_kafka_consumer_partition_lag gauge Number of messages the consumer group is behind by for a partition as reported by Burrow
burrow_kafka_consumer_status gauge The status of the consumer group. It is calculated from the highest status for the individual partitions. Statuses are an index list from NOTFOUND, OK, WARN, ERR, STOP, STALL, REWIND
burrow_kafka_topic_partition_offset gauge Latest offset the topic that Burrow is storing for this partition

etcd_server_read_indexes_failed_total counter The total number of failed read indexes seen.
